<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Cpp on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/cpp/</link><description>Recent content in Cpp on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/cpp/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] C longjmp() Deprecated — Use C++ Exceptions or Error Handling</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/c/longjmp/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/c/longjmp/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-longjmp-deprecated--use-c-exceptions-or-error-handling"&gt;[Solution] C longjmp() Deprecated — Use C++ Exceptions or Error Handling&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;longjmp()&lt;/code&gt; function is deprecated because it performs a non-local jump that bypasses all intermediate stack frames, skipping destructors, resource cleanup, and security checks. It must be used with &lt;code&gt;setjmp()&lt;/code&gt; and is the counterpart to that deprecated function. In C++, use exceptions. In C, use &lt;code&gt;goto&lt;/code&gt; for structured cleanup.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-youll-see"&gt;What You&amp;rsquo;ll See&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Compiler warnings:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;warning: &amp;#39;longjmp&amp;#39; is deprecated: use exceptions or structured error handling
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="why-deprecated"&gt;Why Deprecated&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;longjmp()&lt;/code&gt; is deprecated because:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] C setjmp()/longjmp() Deprecated — Use C++ Exceptions or Proper Error Handling</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/c/setjmp/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/deprecated/c/setjmp/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="solution-c-setjmplongjmp-deprecated--use-c-exceptions-or-proper-error-handling"&gt;[Solution] C setjmp()/longjmp() Deprecated — Use C++ Exceptions or Proper Error Handling&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;setjmp()&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;longjmp()&lt;/code&gt; functions are deprecated in secure coding guidelines because they bypass normal control flow, making programs difficult to reason about and secure. They skip destructor calls, leak resources, and can leave objects in inconsistent states. In C++, use exceptions. In C, use proper error handling with &lt;code&gt;goto&lt;/code&gt; for cleanup or &lt;code&gt;atexit()&lt;/code&gt; handlers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="what-youll-see"&gt;What You&amp;rsquo;ll See&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Compiler warnings with strict security flags:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] R Rcpp Compilation Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/r-rcpp-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/r/r-rcpp-error/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="what-this-error-means"&gt;What This Error Means&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An Rcpp compilation error occurs when C++ code compiled via Rcpp fails to build. This can happen due to syntax errors, missing headers, incorrect function signatures, or linker issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;C++ syntax errors in source files&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing Rcpp header includes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect function signatures for R interface&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing system libraries for linking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;R version or compiler version mismatch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// WRONG: Missing Rcpp include
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// [[Rcpp::export]]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NumericVector &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;addVectors&lt;/span&gt;(NumericVector x, NumericVector y) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; y; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Compilation error
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// CORRECT: Include Rcpp
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;&amp;lt;Rcpp.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;using&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;namespace&lt;/span&gt; Rcpp;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// [[Rcpp::export]]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;NumericVector &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;addVectors&lt;/span&gt;(NumericVector x, NumericVector y) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; x &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; y;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Using Rcpp without proper setup&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rcpp&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sourceCpp&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;code.cpp&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# May fail without proper attributes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Use proper attributes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# In code.cpp:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# // [[Rcpp::depends(Rcpp)]]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# #include &amp;lt;Rcpp.h&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# RCPP_EXPORT_FUNCTION&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# WRONG: Missing linking flags&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rcpp&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;compileAttributes&lt;/span&gt;() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fails on missing libraries&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CORRECT: Add to Makevars&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# ~/.R/Makevars&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# CXXFLAGS += -std=c++11&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Or in DESCRIPTION:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# SystemRequirements: C++11&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-r" data-lang="r"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 1: Source C++ file directly&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rcpp&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;sourceCpp&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;src/mycode.cpp&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 2: Build Rcpp package&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rcpp&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;compileAttributes&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;.&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;system&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;R CMD INSTALL .&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Example 3: Debug compilation&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rcpp&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;::&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;cppFunction&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; int fibonacci(int n) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; if (n &amp;lt;= 1) return n;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; return fibonacci(n-1) + fibonacci(n-2);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fibonacci&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 55&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
